Package com.pandora.calculation.parsers

package com.pandora.calculation.parsers
This package contains utility classes and parsers for handling command-line arguments and parsing species configurations.
Version:
0.0.1
Author:
Wim Joost van Hoek
  • Class
    Description
    CommandLineToolParser
    A utility class for parsing command-line arguments.
    DataContainerParser
    Utility class for parsing bootstrap data from command line arguments.
    FateConfigurationParser
    Utility class for parsing fate configurations from JSON data.
    ModelRunConfigurationParser
     
    Parsable<T>
    The Parsable interface represents an entity capable of parsing command-line arguments into an object of type T.
    SourceConfigurationParser
    Utility class for parsing source configurations from JSON data.
    SpecieConfigurationParser
    Utility class for parsing species configurations from command line arguments.
    TemporalCellDataPointVectorNodeParser
    Utility class for parsing JSON data into TemporalCellDataPointVector objects.
